# Get Those Groceries.

Welcome aboard <%= @user.name %>, Supermarkit is here to try and help make your grocery shopping *simpler*, and *better*.

# We
As a bunch of software students we decided that there must be a more efficient way than using an excel document to keep track of our eating habits. Supermarkit unites you and your friends into groups of shoppers in an attempt to overcome the hastle of keeping things organized and in sync.

# Shop
Supermarkit let's you keep track of the groceries you have bought with ease. It knows that if every week you by *bread*, you're probably going to buy *bread* again and makes it simple to re-add familiar items.

